    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cefbcf1f9f2b4a8e6c76157"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "This kind of non-lethal work might sound innocuous but it is dangerous enough that many [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSolaris7],Solaris VII]] fighters end up being disabled or dead rather than retiring from the stylized fighting of the arenas, Commander {COMMANDER.LastName}.\n\nWhich is exactly with Count von Steffelbus has hired mercenaries for it.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "The Count's ideas are also quite weird... there's been crew discussion.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c2087db9a3c128420d56c94"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cc2970b6d83d5dc3ae2be0e"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "You and the crew does not need to worry about the Count's talk of the grand cosmic order of the universe, or whatever he calls it his interconnectedness theory.\n\nHe may sound and act like an eccentric but quite a practical one since there are rumors within [[DM.Factions[faction_InterstellarExpeditions],IE]] that [[DM.Factions[faction_InterconnectednessUnlimited],IU]] is investing into Kearny-Fuchida research.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c4ff3ea07db98e771c3bc82"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c25109bde4a138c5d0491f2"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreKearnyFuchida],Kearny-Fuchida]]... Alexander that means they are studying JumpShip research?\n\nThat's quite an achievement in the current age of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],lostech]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9ca4d9ad42169ebc6b4d8bbe"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59baac916230356416000354",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c18f87befec685aa192aedf"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "No one knows... a couple of years ago there was an explosion that damaged the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreNewSyrtis],New Syrtis]] shipyards in 3022, which was quite the media event on [[DM.Factions[faction_Davion],Davion]] space.\n\nAnd the rumor mill on Interstellar Expeditions was that it was related to their research, which was confirmed after it has leaked that another of the Count's companies, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGoldenStarEntertainmentGroup],Golden Star Entertainment]], had a lease on the shipyards.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "That's the company that is hiring us.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c64ac765506fc50578cbe7c"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c5ebfab89ee5a1b2fba4a09"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And Interconnectedness Unlimited also owns the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTripleFBurger],Triple-F]] burgers that the crew all enjoy, and the company is massively rich.\n\nPlus the Count's personal philosophy endorses the creation of 'personal action links', which on his case consist of buying all sorts of companies for holistic proposes, including a [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreDGDIA],detective agency]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Holistic? And what does that mean?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cf77f6e8879b8fc7804fd58"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c8728c9bd67dcf304830f7b"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Nothing, don't let Alexander's terms intimidate you {COMMANDER.FirstName}.\n\nWeren't you on your way to an assignment, Alexander?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cb122fba4163cda376df07b"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59baac916230356416000354",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c43e6382f372af6fb4b4780"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Chief Virtanen has ordered me to remove a 'Takashi' in one of our 'Mechs after Count von Steffelbus noticed.\n\nThey are going to use on the final scenes when the Davion rescue force arrives and blasts the polymer coated man's companions into oblivion and they want all Kurita references removed since the 'enemy' now is Liao.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "A 'Takashi'?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 8,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c88be2a3e6f0abcba2f593a"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cdce4085ba24d61c64e563e"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "A painted seated gray rat smoking a cigar.\n\nThat's a 'Takashi'... according to Sumire the design is used by the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreKuritaDCMS],DCMS]]' Legion of Vega regiments and eventually got its nickname because of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTakashiKurita],Takashi Kurita]]'s disdain for the unit.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 9,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c2ea14fa453d23583d378a8"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c57bc0c7f02ae2075c4d7f0"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Well, considering the reputation of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLegionOfVega],Legion of Vega]] being created by Takashi to house all the malcontents and criminals, I am not surprised of either the design or the nickname.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "But why isn't Yang supervising the painting work himself?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c515e74aa288a169ec0e128"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59baac916230356416000354",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd03c6addf519898b47f663"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Because the Chief Mech is currently in a technical discussion with the 'Chancellor of the [[DM.Factions[faction_Liao],Capellan Confederation]]' since every time the actor speaks his lines during the takes, he feels that he needs to correct him about the true '[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMaximillianLiao],Maximillian Liao]]'.\n\nSince Yang once met the actual Chancellor during his [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLiaoCCAF],CCAF]] service, as he keeps reminding everyone in the production team.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 11,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c7d4634a3270aaab3231fbe"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b97f45623035ac140054ca",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c928a59b7fad8647203d6b6"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Alexander, that is Bailey Hudson, one of the biggest holovid actors in the Federated Suns... Yang can't just go barging into Interconnectedness' production like that and tell them what to do...\n\nWhat has Count von Steffelbus said about it?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 12,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c1a048e3c6410a5ffcabfff"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59baac916230356416000354",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c8c88176ca4296f47583180"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "The Count has kept a hands off approach in the situation so far, as long as Yang keeps the 'Mechs ready for the production.\n\nWell, I'm off to the Mech Bay, good luck Commander with the next scenes.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
